 1. Change `var headers = sheet.getRange(13, 8).getValues();` to `var headers = sheet.getRange(13, 1, 1, sheet.getLastColumn());`
 2.  Change `Utilities.formatDate(new Date(), timezone, timestamp_format);` to `Utilities.formatDate(now, timezone, timestamp_format);`. No need to create a new Date() object.
 3. Use the `e` event object to detect current changes. Change `var actRng = SpreadsheetApp.getActiveRange();` to `var actRng = e.range;`
